placed on the front leg,

47
00:03:44,281 --> 00:03:47,881
momentum from the jump
powers a strong drive.

48
00:03:47,915 --> 00:03:50,948
What's more, by
maintaining contact

49
00:03:50,981 --> 00:03:53,781
with the ball on
the follow through,

50
00:03:53,815 --> 00:03:57,715
