00:16:53,017 --> 00:16:54,183
Stop acting confrontational.

274
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:06,417
Both players, take
your positions.

275
00:17:06,450 --> 00:17:08,250
-What's that crazy
guy's problem?

276
00:17:08,283 --> 00:17:10,583
Is he trying to pick a
fight from the start?

277
00:17:10,617 --> 00:17:13,617
-It looks like he's
not gonna let it be.

278
00:17:13,650 --> 00:17:14,283
-Argh!

279
00:17:14,317 --> 00:17:16,117
