301
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:35,950
That wasn't the
serve I expected.

302
00:18:43,817 --> 00:18:44,750
-Good one.

303
00:18:44,783 --> 00:18:46,683
It's a drop volley.

304
00:18:46,717 --> 00:18:47,150
-Heh.

305
00:18:50,117 --> 00:18:56,850
You better not underestimate me.

306
00:19:05,783 --> 00:19:15,683
-Drive A.

307
00:19:15,717 --> 00:19:16,417
-Akutsu, no!

308
00:19:20,750 --> 00:19:23,883
-Hitting a drive volley
from that short distance,

309
00:19:23,917 --> 00:19:25,683
that's intense.

310
00:19:25,717 --> 00:19:28,550
-He sure is his father's son.

311
00:19:28,583 --> 00:19:30,417
One can certainly see that.

312
00:19:30,450 --> 00:19:32,817
-Uh.

313
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:33,883
-What a riot.

