00:19:42,917 --> 00:19:43,517
-Oops.

317
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:45,250
Sorry about that.

318
00:19:45,283 --> 00:19:48,050
But it's just
that, you shouldn't

319
00:19:48,083 --> 00:19:50,317
underrate tennis the way you do.

320
00:20:04,750 --> 00:20:07,717
[laughing]

321
00:20:22,691 --> 00:20:25,324
[theme music]

322
00:20:54,058 --> 00:20:58,091
-I'm Akutsu, a ninth grader
from Yamabuki Junior High.

323
00:20:58,124 --> 00:20:59,758
