324
00:20:59,791 --> 00:21:02,558
Are you telling me I'm
a disgrace to the game?

325
00:21:02,591 --> 00:21:06,391
I think those who only
talk the talk are sissies.

326
00:21:06,424 --> 00:21:07,224
Hey, punk.

327
00:21:07,258 --> 00:21:08,491
I'll play you, as I promised.

328
00:21:08,524 --> 00:21:10,758
If you have any problems
with that, all you have to do

329
00:21:10,791 --> 00:21:13,291
is beat me first.

330
00:21:13,324 --> 00:21:16,291
Next on "The Prince of
Tennis," A Devil on the Court.

331
00:21:16,324 --> 00:21:19,491
And don't even think
about ordering me around.

